    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Pangfeng Liu</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:130px;\"><a href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/images/2002%20IOI/page_01.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/0/08/PenfengLiu.JPG\" width=\"128\" height=\"96\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:PenfengLiu.JPG\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Pangfeng Liu <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Pangfeng Liu</b>,<br />\na Taiwanese computer scientist and professor at the Department of Information Engineering and Computer Science <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> at the <a href=\"/National_Taiwan_University\" title=\"National Taiwan University\">National Taiwan University</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> . His research interests covers distributed algorithms, <a href=\"/Parallel_Search\" title=\"Parallel Search\">Parallel Search</a> as well as <a href=\"/Chinese_Chess\" title=\"Chinese Chess\">Computer Chinese Chess</a>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2005_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2005 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pangfeng_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pangfeng_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.cs.cmu.edu/~svc/talks/20061206-bhatt.html\">Sandeep Bhatt</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/indices/a-tree/a/Aiello:William.html\">William Aiello</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>An atomic model for message passing</i>, SIAM Journal on Computing, vol. 31(1), pp. 67-85, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/papers/SIAM%20atomic%20model.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>Broadcast scheduling optimization for heterogeneous cluster systems</i>, Journal of Algorithms, vol. 42, pp. 135-152</li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan-Jan_Wu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jan-Jan Wu (page does not exist)\">Jan-Jan Wu</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Chih-Hsuae_Yang&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Chih-Hsuae Yang (page does not exist)\">Chih-Hsuae Yang</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i>Locality-Preserving Dynamic Load Balancing for Data-Parallel Applications on Distributed-Memory Multiprocessors</i>. JOURNAL OF INFORMATION SCIENCE AND ENGINEERING 18, 1037-1048, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/papers/JISE%20WBRT.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2005_...\">2005 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pangfeng_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2005 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-75538-8_9\">Abstracting Knowledge from Annotated Chinese-Chess Game Records</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2006\" title=\"CG 2006\">CG 2006</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2008</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-540-87608-3_17\">Knowledge Inferencing on Chinese Chess Endgames</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2008\" title=\"CG 2008\">CG 2008</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Conflict Resolution of Chinese Chess Endgame Knowledge Base</i>. <a href=\"/Advances_in_Computer_Games_12\" title=\"Advances in Computer Games 12\">Advances in Computer Games 12</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ticc.uvt.nl/icga/acg12/proceedings/Contribution108.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Hung-Jui_Chang\" title=\"Hung-Jui Chang\">Hung-Jui Chang</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jan-Jan_Wu&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jan-Jan Wu (page does not exist)\">Jan-Jan Wu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>Job Scheduling Techniques for Distributed Systems with Heterogeneous Processor Cardinality</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ispan2009.comm.ccu.edu.tw/\">ISPAN'2009</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.iis.sinica.edu.tw/papers/wuj/9213-F.pdf\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Jian-Yu_Chen&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Jian-Yu Chen (page does not exist)\">Jian-Yu Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Jr-Chang_Chen\" title=\"Jr-Chang Chen\">Jr-Chang Chen</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/4085558478885735/\">An Intelligent Tutoring System of Chinese Chess</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/conf/ieaaie/ieaaie2009.html#ChenCCHLH09\">IEA/AIE 2009</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pangfeng_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.springerlink.com/content/6374711454584j73/\">Knowledge Abstraction in Chinese Chess Endgame Databases</a></i>. <a href=\"/CG_2010\" title=\"CG 2010\">CG 2010</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Bo-Nian_Chen\" title=\"Bo-Nian Chen\">Bo-Nian Chen</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Pangfeng Liu</a>, <a href=\"/Shun-Chin_Hsu\" title=\"Shun-Chin Hsu\">Shun-Chin Hsu</a>, <a href=\"/Tsan-sheng_Hsu\" title=\"Tsan-sheng Hsu\">Tsan-sheng Hsu</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0950705111002565\">Aggregating consistent endgame knowledge in Chinese Chess</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/db/journals/kbs/kbs34.html#ChenLHH12\">Knowledge Based Systems, Vol. 34</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pangfeng_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/\">Pangfeng Liu Homepage</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pangfeng_Liu&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/gallery.htm\">Pangfeng Liu - 2002 International Olympiad in Informatics, Yong-In, Korea.</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/\">Department of Information Engineering and Computer Science</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/\">Pangfeng Liu Homepage</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.csie.ntu.edu.tw/~pangfeng/publication.php\">Journal papers - Pangfeng Liu Hsu</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.informatik.uni-trier.de/~ley/pers/hd/l/Liu:Pangfeng\">dblp: Pangfeng Liu</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 202603